queries.sql: SELECT `lrfoims_carts`.*, SUM(lrfoims_carts.quantity * m.price) as total_price, SUM(lrfoims_carts.quantity * m.price) - (SUM(lrfoims_carts.quantity * m.price) * oud.discount_amount) + o.delivery_fee - o.coupon_discount as total_amount_bill, (SUM(lrfoims_carts.quantity * m.price) + o.delivery_fee) - o.coupon_discount as total_amount_bill_no_discount, (SUM(lrfoims_carts.quantity * m.price) / 1.12 * 0.12) as total_amount_discount_with_vat, (SUM(lrfoims_carts.quantity * m.price) / 1.12 * 0.12) as total_amount_regular_customer_with_vat, SUM(lrfoims_carts.quantity * m.price) * oud.discount_amount as total_amount_user_discount_without_vat, `o`.`order_status_id`, `o`.`c_cash`, `o`.`c_balance`, `o`.`total_amount`, `o`.`discount_amount` FROM `lrfoims_carts` JOIN `lrfoims_orders` as `o` ON `lrfoims_carts`.`order_id` = `o`.`id` JOIN `lrfoims_menus` as `m` ON `lrfoims_carts`.`menu_id` = `m`.`id` LEFT JOIN `lrfoims_order_user_discounts` as `oud` ON `o`.`order_user_discount_id` = `oud`.`id` WHERE `lrfoims_carts`.`status` = 'a' AND `lrfoims_carts`.`deleted_at` IS NULL GROUP BY `lrfoims_carts`.`order_id`
